# Introduction to SwiftUI

In this exercise, we want to implement a simple Hello World SwiftUI example via Xcode.

**You have the following tasks:**

1. [task][Implement Greeting.swift](testGreeting)
Implement the class `Greeting.swift`.

2. [task][Implement UI](testGreetingUI)
Implement the UI and verify that the shown TextView contains "Hello, world!".
